Usage: MHOP [-F] [-A] [#channel]
  Mass halfops channel

  If passed -F only friends with the H flag set will be halfopped.
  -A will halfop all users.

See also:
  MDHOP
  MOP
  MREOP
  MDOP
  MASSV
